ommuters in western suburbs waiting for improved connectivity.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/chennai-metro-phase-ii-delayed-passengers-left-waiting-for-train-operations/131848011?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-57818/131848011.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}]}